---
title: Mighty Prawn & Bean Rice Bowl with Avocado Salsa & Lemony Mayonnaise
description: This dish is a true feast for champions! This zingy combo will give you the boost you need, with seared chilli prawns, a fresh avo salsa and a lemony mayo. Fluffy rice and kidney beans provide a satiating base for all those bright flavours, creating a perfectly balanced meal.
